---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy | Akhil Arun Menon" description="Privacy information for the Akhil Arun Menon professional portfolio website.">
  <PageHero eyebrow="Privacy" title="How this website handles information" description="A concise statement covering contact forms, analytics, comments and external links." />
  <section class="section"><div class="narrow prose">
    <h2>Contact and subscription forms</h2>
    <p>Information submitted through the website is used only to respond to enquiries or record subscription interest. The static website sends form submissions through FormSubmit to the published contact email address.</p>
    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>Google Analytics is loaded only after a valid measurement ID is configured by the site owner. The implementation requests anonymised IP handling. Analytics data is used to understand page usage and improve the website.</p>
    <h2>Comments</h2>
    <p>Blog comments use Utterances and GitHub Issues. Visitors who comment are subject to GitHub's authentication and privacy terms.</p>
    <h2>External links</h2>
    <p>The website links to LinkedIn, GitHub, WhatsApp and other external services. Their privacy practices apply after leaving this website.</p>
    <h2>Portfolio content</h2>
    <p>Confidential client data is not published. Data visualisation demonstrations use simulated or open data. Student photographs are not included.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this statement may be sent to <a href="mailto:akhil.menon94@gmail.com">akhil.menon94@gmail.com</a>.</p>
  </div></section>
</BaseLayout>
